collection.name: Voxies
collection.description:
Voxies are cute, lovable and collectible 3d voxel buddies, that live and play on the Ethereum blockchain. There are only 10,000 Voxies in existence and no two Voxies are identical. Lots of random properties and fun traits make each Voxie cute, unique and sometimes rare!

Voxies are not just a collectible but are also the first and only NFT to be fully integrated with a playable RPG turn-based tactical game. Bring your owned Voxies to life in Voxie Tactics as you collect, battle, and earn rewards in the Voxiverse. VOXEL tokens are used as the currency in Voxie Tactics and used to buy/trade on the Voxies marketplace.
